item.description:
Pay experienced programmers to develop your application.

We have a marketplace category in the Discord server - KeyAuth

If you’re a user looking to pay programmers, look at the #offers channel. If you’re a programmer looking to make money, look at the #apply-for-merchant channel.

Merchants go through a screening process to ensure they’re reputable. Thus, you can be quite confident you won’t be scammed or be sold stolen code.
